</li><li> Ros&eacute; Mulan from <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VisualNovel/SpiritHunterNG" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VisualNovel/SpiritHunterNG">Spirit Hunter: NG</a></em> has stage magician as her claimed profession, though she states it's merely a side gig for her true role as a supernatural savant. When she's able to pick locks, she claims it's from her experience as a magician, though there's clearly more to it than that.
</li></ul></div>
